## Phased Roadmap
 
### Phase 1 — MVP: Chat with Memory (Weeks 1–4)
- Upload PDF, DOCX, TXT files → chunked and embedded into Qdrant
- Ask questions grounded in your documents (RAG)
- Conversation history persists across sessions (PostgreSQL)
- Basic user fact and preference extraction
- Chainlit web UI
- Full LangSmith tracing from day one
### Phase 2 — Voice + Better Memory (Weeks 5–8)
- Voice input via Whisper (speech-to-text)
- Voice output via ElevenLabs (text-to-speech)
- Memory agent that actively updates user profile mid-conversation
- URL and web page ingestion
- Style and tone adaptation based on learned preferences
### Phase 3 — Proactive + Scale (Weeks 9–12)
- Proactive surfacing — agent surfaces relevant content unprompted
- Video ingestion via Whisper transcription pipeline
- Structured data ingestion (CSV, JSON)
- Azure infrastructure hardened for production
- DSPy reinforcement learning module for objective optimization
- Control plane — guardrails, forbidden actions, approval workflows
- Databricks integration for large-scale data pipelines
